<DOCNO> NYT19991024.0029 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-24 01:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6679 &Cx1f; tic-z
r a BC-BACTERIA-COLONIES-AZR     10-24 0464
