<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-24 18:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6830 &Cx1f; tad-z
u a BC-CRASH-METAL25-COX-1ST     10-24 1726
