<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-24 20:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6925 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-SAFIRE-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      10-24 0746
